<div class="wrap">	<h1>Description</h1>		<p>1.plugin will list alphabets A-Z.</p>		<p>2.When user hovers over any alphabet it will lists posts, pages, custom post types title starting with</p>		the alphabet user hovers.		<p>3.The titles will have link and it will take user to single page.</p>			<h2>How to Use</h2>		You need to use shortcodes to embed a listing in your post/page	<br /><br />	<strong>1.copy and paste the shortcode where you want to display alphabet listing</strong><br/>	<ul>		<li>1. [atoz]</li>	</ul>	<strong>2.Go to settings there you can set look and feel of the plugin </strong><br/>	<b>There you can set</b>	<ul>		<li>Listing title </li>		<li>Listing Type(you need type "post" or "page" default is post)</li>		<li>Background Color</li>		<li>Text Color</li>		<li>Alphabet Background Color</li>			</ul></div>